  "title": "Service Sales Engineer (Technical Sales Engineer)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Well Established Company</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Basic $3000 - $3500 + Incentive + Variable Bonus</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working location: Tuas</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working days:</strong> <strong>Monday to Friday (8am to 5pm), Saturday (8am to 12pm)</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Finding and securing new customers</li>\n  <li>Attend to client enquiry, site visit, understand, communicate product value, provide solution, negotiating and close deal</li>\n  <li>Track customer interactions and sales data, coordinate efforts with marketing and stay informed about market trends to drive revenue and achieve company growth</li>\n  <li>Other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess minimum Nitec/Diploma qualification with minimum 1-2 years of relevant experience</li>\n  <li>Possess with electrical and crane/hoist basic knowledge will be added advantage</li>\n  <li>Preferable possess Singapore driving license</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now </strong>button with the following information in the resume</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving</li>\n  <li>Date of availability</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>LIONG ZHAO GUAN (R22107632)</p>\n<p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
